headline: Goldman Sachs Lowers its Price Target on BXP, Inc. (BXP) to $72 and Keeps a Neutral Rating
summary: BXP, Inc. (NYSE:BXP) is included in our list of Real Estate Investing for Beginners: 10 Best Stocks to Buy. On February 5, 2026, Goldman Sachs lowered its price target on BXP, Inc. (NYSE:BXP) to $72 from $75 and kept a Neutral rating. The firm updated its model following fourth-quarter results, noting progress on property dispositions […]

headline: Stock Market Suffers AI-Inspired Meltdown. The Real World Wins Again.
